text: Tau (Τ or τ) is the 19th letter of the Greek alphabet. Tau may also refer to: ==Mathematics== * Tau (mathematical constant), a constant equal to (6.28318...) ==Science and technology== * TAU (spacecraft), a proposal to send a space probe to a thousand units from the Earth * Tau (particle), also called Tau lepton, an elementary particle * Tau emerald, a species of dragonfly * Tau neutrino a particle * Tau protein, a biochemical protein * Tau, the standard astronomical abbreviation for Taurus (constellation) ==Other== * Tau Day
